Quantile Regression

Introduction

This example is from MICROECONOMETRICS USING STATA (A. C. Cameron and P. K. Trivedi) R package required for quantile regression is {guantreg}

Loading data

To load data in Stata format, we can use read.dta from {foreign}

dta <- read.dta("dta/mus03data.dta")
apply(dta, 2,function(x) sum(is.na(x))) # number of NA in each column
